                    "body": "{quote}So the `pa.SerializationContext()` won't work with Table.from_pandas?\r\n{quote}\r\nThat feature is deprecated since pickle now works just as well.\r\n{quote}If not, can I make this into a feature request for that feature?\r\n{quote}\r\nCould you describe the feature you have in mind? A mock code example showing how it would work would be helpful. Are you suggesting that Table.from_pandas should automatically pickle columns of dtype object?",
